data.description: UNIQUE OPPORTUNITY - TURN OF THE CENTURY VICTORIAN HOME. A true classic... spacious, vintage home perfectly located ready for your personal touches. 4000+ Sq. ft. with 2 car garage, 4-6 bedrooms, formal living rm, den/office, formal dining, large family rm, beautiful custom bar/lounge w/ custom built-in cabinetry, gorgeous hardwood flooring throughout, many original wood moldings, full basement, and privately fenced in back yard! No development/no dues. Minutes to downtown Hawley and premier Lake Wallenpaupack in the heart of the Poconos. Minutes to Honesdale, PA for convenient shopping and daily needs. This original home is truly a must see!, Beds Description: 2+BED 2nd, Baths: 1 Bath Level 2, Baths: 1/2 Bath Lev 1, Baths: 1/2 Bath Lev 2,  Eating Area: Formal DN Room,  Eating Area: Semi-Modern KT
